{"tid":1824824,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"老任持續發威中！任天堂吃走日本遊戲主機8成市場","createTime":"2020-01-14T18:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T18:35:29.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c226de58cc7fa9d26f58e9db14e2938ddcaff8e2","tid":1824824,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"老任持續發威中！任天堂吃走日本遊戲主機8成市場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NWRhOdrPa3oGMuLK3ELAYA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1OS45MzE2MjM5MzE2MjM5/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ZEPFQZxR8MlXGrA_3PBLYg--~B/aD02NTg7dz0xMTcwO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/game_nownews_com_902/6c54447e95d85e7d6c663e04a0bf2e4a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNWRhOdrPa3oGMuLK3ELAYA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1OS45MzE2MjM5MzE2MjM5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZEPFQZxR8MlXGrA_3PBLYg--~B%2FaD02NTg7dz0xMTcwO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fgame_nownews_com_902%2F6c54447e95d85e7d6c663e04a0bf2e4a&h=f4e9a45e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從2017年Switch正式在全球上市後，不僅已經在全球賣出超過4167萬台，任天堂大本營日本更是賣到超誇張。近日就有調查報告指出，日本的遊戲主機市場（含掌機）超過8成已經被任天堂給吃下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jyMHx4ISVCAoX7aIvIaLuA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTU5MC4yMDg3Mjg2NTI3NTE1/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/game_nownews_com_902/5f5b8f828c8d1f965d1dc0e64ad59d67\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjyMHx4ISVCAoX7aIvIaLuA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTU5MC4yMDg3Mjg2NTI3NTE1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fgame_nownews_com_902%2F5f5b8f828c8d1f965d1dc0e64ad59d67&h=d00e3da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獨立記者 Oscar Lemaire 近日在推特上引用了日本Fami通的數據並經過整理後，表示2019年任天堂佔據了日本80%的遊戲主機市場，其中76%是Switch、3%左右為3DS；而對比之下，對手Sony的PS4僅占20%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Uu1WndyK7H9rfbievkDuUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTI5MC42NjM4NTY2OTEyNTM5NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/game_nownews_com_902/c67a1541a1fcfa56e243dfd5e5730d2a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUu1WndyK7H9rfbievkDuUQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTI5MC42NjM4NTY2OTEyNTM5NQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fgame_nownews_com_902%2Fc67a1541a1fcfa56e243dfd5e5730d2a&h=22ee2e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而銷售額部分，Switch 在2019年的銷售額比起2018年成長了約29%。所以即使PS4和3DS分別衰退29%和66%，Switch依舊獨挑大樑，撐起了日本市場銷售額的重責大任。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UCy6NqVFA4xn30fnXHaTsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTI1OS43MzcyMjYyNzczNzIyNg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/game_nownews_com_902/3a2c74bc0899ef1e280695ae80911ec5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUCy6NqVFA4xn30fnXHaTsg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTI1OS43MzcyMjYyNzczNzIyNg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fgame_nownews_com_902%2F3a2c74bc0899ef1e280695ae80911ec5&h=384419d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而把時間軸拉長的話，Switch表現依舊亮眼。 Oscar Lemaire 指出，從1999年到2019年來看，2019年甚至是任天堂主機銷售最好的一年，對於一家在主機界發展已久的公司來說，這是一項相當難得的事情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z97XkSpqrFgRJhepbl0JeA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMxNC40NTA4NjcwNTIwMjMx/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/game_nownews_com_902/3541fa264a391ddff7e65b281c1ae886\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz97XkSpqrFgRJhepbl0JeA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMxNC40NTA4NjcwNTIwMjMx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fgame_nownews_com_902%2F3541fa264a391ddff7e65b281c1ae886&h=81ae0ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞來源為「NOW電玩」"},{"pid":"33249929bfb40e2222fe8734d20d092a22f9f20c","tid":1824824,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:03:24.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報A1頭條：影相都拉 青年警署被虐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5db11475d565c2f081c90a4902532747195afe67","tid":1824824,"uid":98899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾Tegra X1 + 奶共<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"db827a6c402d013ee229ac0fc1c62de978d60a00","tid":1824824,"uid":282535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"單計2019銷售量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS4同3DS係幾多年前嘅產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要買都一早買咗啦"},{"pid":"d94326cb41141a708e69e1a3f4fcbd50a47ee58c","tid":1824824,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:23:42.000Z","msg":"ps4到末期啦"},{"pid":"e138112a230f5599be009a8489310fe4c95c3129","tid":1824824,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5db11475d565c2f081c90a4902532747195afe67","tid":1824824,"uid":98899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:09:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾Tegra X1 + 奶共<br />\n不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T18:35:29.000Z","msg":"三間加steam都奶<br />\n咪打機啦on9仔"}]}